; Real-browser e2e for the site example, written with the fennec-e2e DSL. The suites
; (site.ml, …) register their tests; run.ml boots the server + browser and runs them.
; NOT part of `dune test` (needs a system Chrome); run via ./run.sh. -linkall so every
; suite module's registration runs even though run.ml never references them by name.
(executable
 (name run)
 (modules run site)
 (libraries fennec-e2e)
 (link_flags (-linkall)))
